### Phase 0 — Lift-off (GET /decolamos)
GET http://localhost:8080/decolamos

###

### Phase 0 — List aircraft (empty or populated)
GET http://localhost:8080/aircraft

###

### Phase 0 — Create aircraft (minimal payload)
POST http://localhost:8080/aircraft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "F-16C",
  "manufacturer": "Lockheed Martin",
  "year": 1991 
}

###

### Phase 0 — Create aircraft (invalid year — too old)
POST http://localhost:8080/aircraft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "Ancient",
  "manufacturer": "Wright Brothers",
  "year": 1880
}

###

### Phase 0 — Create aircraft (invalid year — future)
POST http://localhost:8080/aircraft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "Future Fighter",
  "manufacturer": "Fictional Inc",
  "year": 2050
}

###
